001
002package com.commercetools.api.models;
003
004public interface Versioned<T> extends Identifiable<T> {
005    @Override
006    String getId();
007
008    Long getVersion();
009
010    /**
011     * Creates a versioned that only contains the id and the version.
012     * @param versioned the template object to use its ID and version
013     * @param <T> The type which has an ID and version.
014     * @return versioned
015     */
016    static <T> Versioned<T> of(final Versioned<T> versioned) {
017        return of(versioned.getId(), versioned.getVersion());
018    }
019
020    static <T> Versioned<T> of(final String id, final long version) {
021        return new SimpleVersioned<>(id, version);
022    }
023}
